<br>
Here's the problem.<br>
<br>
Say you wanna fight Gorenaire.  Which form do you use?  Do you go to fire form and have 0 cold resist and get killed really quick by her spells?  Or do you go to ice form and resist everything she throws but only cast ice based spells back (which she IS going to resist, see comment above)?<br>
<br>
